  <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Full board with complimentary soft drinks at the <a data-udi="umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13}" title="Harriniva Adventure Resort"><span>Harriniva</span> Adventure Resort</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486}" title="Jeris Lakeside Resort">Jeris Lakeside Resort</a></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Package with excursions and a meeting with Santa included </span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Stay above the Arctic Circle</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Remote wilderness locations</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">On the Finnish-Swedish border</span></li>
</ul>
<p>Muonio is the ideal resort if you are looking for a wilderness retreat in Lapland and the perfect place to meet Santa. This resort really allows you to appreciate the beauty Lapland has to offer. Given the remote location of Muonio, the skies are especially clear, giving you the chance to witness the magical Northern Lights. </p>
<h2>What's included in an Inghams holiday to Muonio</h2>
<p>On an Ingham's Lapland holiday to Muonio you will have everything included for a magical break in Finland.</p>
<ul>
<li><span>Full board with complimentary coffee and tea in the hotel main restaurant at the </span><a data-udi="umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13}" title="Harriniva Adventure Resort"><span>Harriniva</span> Adventure Resort</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486}" title="Jeris Lakeside Resort" data-anchor="#">Jeris Lakeside Resort</a></li>
<li>Excursions including Santa visit, snowmobiling, reindeer safari and husky safari</li>
<li>Flights </li>
<li>Transfers to / from Kittila</li>
<li>Arctic thermal suits and boots (3 years and over - these breaks are not recommended for infants)</li>
<li>Inghams rep service</li>
</ul>
<h2>Winter wonderland</h2>
<p>Muonio is set in the remote Finnish fells, next to the beautiful <span>Muonionjoki River - Europes</span> largest free-flowing river separating Finland and Sweden. Located 200 kilometers above the Arctic Circle, staying in the Muonio area allows you to fully embrace the peace and quiet of the real <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Finnish Lapland</a>. <span>The landscape is dominated by snow-covered forests, frozen lakes, and glistening fells, creating an authentic winter wonderland during the colder months. </span></p>
<h2><span>Arctic adventures</span></h2>
<p><span>Experience the wonders of <a data-udi="umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a> this winter season in the magical <a data-udi="umb://document/e503cfe5221245848fdc35484972181c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e503cfe5221245848fdc35484972181c}" title="Santa Breaks in Muonio">Muonio</a>. Experience a world of enchantment with a variety of winter activities all included with your Ingham's <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Santa Break</a> package. Feel the thrill as you slide down the slopes on a toboggan, race through the snowy fells on a snowmobile, embark on a magical husky safari through the magical untouched landscape or take a serene reindeer sleigh ride through the sparkling forests.  You can also bake traditional Finnish gingerbread cookies, or craft your very own Christmas decorations to remember your enchanting trip to Lapland. The highlight of the day is experiencing the magic of meeting Santa in his hidden cabin, nestled among snow-covered trees and glistening icicles.  Each family will have a special meeting with Santa, where the children will receive a small gift. With enough Christmas magic, y</span><span>ou may even be lucky enough to </span>encounter the mystical Northern Lights, a magical display of dancing colours that paint the night sky with hues of emerald green, sapphire blue, and fiery red, it really is the greatest light show on earth. </p>
<h2>Where to stay in Muonio</h2>
<p>We offer two all inclusive packages in either the traditional <a data-udi="umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a3eb0cda4234774a1795ec38e361e13}" title="Harriniva Adventure Resort" data-anchor="#">Harriniva Wilderness Hotel</a>, or the remote <a data-udi="umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486}" title="Jeris Lakeside Resort" data-anchor="#">Jeris Lakeside Resort.</a> The accommodation is furnished to a high standard, perfect for families looking for traditional Finnish accommodation, plus all of your excursions are included.  </p>
<p>Still got a question? See our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/guest-services/frequently-asked-questions#santa-breaks" data-anchor="#santa-breaks">Santa Break FAQs</a>.</p>]]></description>
